snippet.textDisplay: He is a Remnant. He planted his seed many many years ago-Has and Forever will grow. His music was Powerful but yet he was so Humble. I had to comment again.- Just beautiful. Then I started hearing it over and over again as remakes - Preteen, Teenager,and as an a Adult .Gospel, Country, Rap- You name it. This is what it Truly means to be " Fruitful and Multiply". I named the people he touched in music but he didn't care about that- My point was Eveyone Loved him. He was in a Class of his own.
